---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'Codex for (almost) everything | OpenAI';
const description = 'OpenAI 发布 Codex 重大更新，支持计算机操作、图像生成、PR 审查等更多功能。';
---

<Layout 
  title={title}
  description={description}
  type="article"
  publishedTime="2026-04-16"
  tags={["AI-Agents", "Agent-Economy", "Future-of-Work"]}
>
  <article class="article-content">
    <h1 class="lang-content lang-zh active">OpenAI 发布 Codex 重大更新</h1>
    <h1 class="lang-content lang-en">Codex for (almost) everything | OpenAI</h1>
    
    <time datetime="2026-04-16">2026-04-16</time>
    
    <div class="lang-content lang-zh active">
      <p>OpenAI 发布 Codex 重大更新，支持计算机操作、图像生成、PR 审查等更多功能。Codex 现在可以操作你的电脑，与更多日常工具和应用协同工作，生成图像，记住你的偏好，从之前的操作中学习，并承担持续和可重复的工作。</p>
      <p><a href="https://openai.com/index/codex-for-almost-everything/" target="_blank">阅读原文</a></p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="lang-content lang-en">
      <p>OpenAI releases a major update to Codex, making it a more powerful partner for developers. Codex can now operate your computer, work with more tools and apps, generate images, remember preferences, learn from previous actions, and take on ongoing work.</p>
      <p><a href="https://openai.com/index/codex-for-almost-everything/" target="_blank">Read the full article</a></p>
    </div>
    
    <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to articles</a>
  </article>
</Layout>
